<div id="body" class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
      <h2>Send a Recommendation</h2>
      <p>Got an idea how I can make this site better? Let me know!</p>
      <p>Having a problem with something? Let me know and I'll try my best to get back to you and help figure out the problem!</p>
      <form novalidate>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Subject</label>
          <input ng-model="subject" class="form-control">
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
          <label>Content</label>
          <textarea ng-model="content" class="form-control"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button ng-click="send()" type="submit" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg">Send</button>
      </form>
      <hr>
      <p>Rather contact me directly? Send an email to <a href="mailto:anthonydresserdev@gmail.com">anthonydresserdev@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
